[1] Rabies - New York
Date: 6 Aug 2016
Source: WBNG.com [edited]
http://www.wbng.com/news/local/Skunk-tests-positive-for-rabies-in-Delhi-389389911.html


The skunk found in Delhi [Delaware county, New York] was sent to the New York State Rabies lab for testing, according to Delaware County [NY] Public Health Services.

One adult did come in contact with the animal and is undergoing treatment, officials said.

